TODO: Complete this file

1) Install prerequisites (if required):
---------------------------------------
sudo apt-get install libmicrohttpd-dev
sudo apt-get install libjson-c-dev
sudo apt-get install libssl-dev
sudo apt-get install make

2) Build
--------
make

3) Install
----------
sudo make install

4) For new installations only:
------------------------------

  4.a) Create a clean servers.hhl7 and configure for use, e.g: 
  --------------------------------------
  sudo mv /usr/local/hhl7/conf/servers.hhl7.example /usr/local/hhl7/conf/servers.hhl7
  vi /usr/local/hhl7/conf/servers.hhl7

  4.b) Make ssh keys (example, please be secure):
  -----------------------------------------------
  openssl genrsa -out server.key 1024
  openssl req -days 365 -out server.pem -new -x509 -key server.key
  sudo mv server.* /usr/local/hhl7/certs/
